      "beat_id": "B04",
      "act": "THE PROBLEM",
      "estimated_duration_s": 8.5,
      "narration_text": "In human communication, clear writing is evidence of clear thinking. This heuristic is reliable \u2014 and it is exactly what AI has broken.",
